WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:47.000
 Remove bolts from crankcase. 

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:54.000
 Disassemble crankcase cover. 

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:00.000
 Install blocking key. 

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:13.000
 Remove the coupling housing nut. 

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:20.000
 Disassemble the clutch housing. 

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:25.000
 Install blocking key. 

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:36.000
 Remove the nut. 

00:01:46.000 --> 00:02:00.000
 Put new V-belt in rear coupling. (Note: pull the bowls of the pulley as far apart as possible. This is difficult !!) 

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:06.000
 Replace the clutch pulley. 

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:23.000
 Fit nut. 

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:24.000
 Fit nut. 

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:28.000
 Fit V-belt on crankshaft. 

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:33.000
 Mount cooling fin vario. 

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:46.000
 Fit washers and nut. 

00:02:46.000 --> 00:03:16.000
 Install locking key and tighten nut. 

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:23.000
 Install crankcase cover. 

00:03:23.000 --> 00:04:03.000
 Fit bolts. 

